{
  "page": "Artos Flint",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Flint_of_the_mountains\" title=\"House Flint of the mountains\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/50px-None.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/75px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/100px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Artos Flint</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Flint_of_the_mountains\" title=\"House Flint of the mountains\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/50px-None.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/75px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/100px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Flint_of_the_mountains\" title=\"House Flint of the mountains\">House Flint of the mountains</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northern_mountain_clans\" title=\"Northern mountain clans\">Northern mountain clans</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Torghen_Flint\" title=\"Torghen Flint\">Torghen Flint</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Artos Flint</b> is the second son of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Torghen_Flint\" title=\"Torghen Flint\">Torghen Flint</a>, known as The Flint, or Old Flint clan chief of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Flint_of_the_mountains\" title=\"House Flint of the mountains\">first Flints</a>, a mountain clan in the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">North</a>. He is the half-brother of Black <a href=\"/index.php/Donnel_Flint\" title=\"Donnel Flint\">Donnel Flint</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_With_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance With Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Artos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Artos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Artos_Flint&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_With_Dragons\"><i>A Dance With Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Artos_Flint&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance With Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Artos is among the Flints who march with <a href=\"/index.php/King\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King\">King</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>'s army to retake <a href=\"/index.php/Deepwood_Motte\" title=\"Deepwood Motte\">Deepwood Motte</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Asha Greyjoy</a>. After the <a href=\"/index.php/Fight_by_Deepwood_Motte\" title=\"Fight by Deepwood Motte\">battle</a>, Artos sits upon Stannis' war council alongside several other Northern clansmen. He endorses the plan for Stannis' army to march on the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\">Boltons</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>, noting that it is only a three-hundred mile march to the castle.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Artos\">Quotes by Artos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Artos_Flint&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Artos\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/R%27hllor\" title=\"R&#39;hllor\">R'hllor</a> will doom us.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Artos_Flint&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />first wife</td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Torghen_Flint\" title=\"Torghen Flint\">Torghen</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />second wife</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1p